originalText.text: Dr. Babaeva was wonderful in her level of care in every way. I was very concerned about lab results and needed tests done before the holidays and she made it a point to call me directly herself to discuss my lab results before the holidays to put my mind at ease. She is very professional and takes the time with patients to help them which isn’t always the case. I’ve changed my primary care provider to her now as a result of her great level of care for her patients.
